<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1439,258,604]" box="[198,1437,498,524]" pageId="8" pageNumber="213">
Remarks: There are several more abyssal records of 
<taxonomicName box="[815,1061,498,523]" class="Polyplacophora" family="Leptochitonidae" genus="Leptochiton" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidopleurida" pageId="8" pageNumber="213" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="alveolus">
